{"tid":1436701,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個方法逼狗出不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:08:24.000Z","uid":62776,"like":154,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"93d76287bf6b0ce8629b71ce64b2f419c196f399","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"既然機場係佢地弱點<br />\n打狗打痛腳<br />\n以後但凡任何遊行或者集會唔出不反對通知書既<br />\n就自動當轉去機場<br />\n反正佢依家批得既都係室外集會<br />\n我不如去個有冷氣，wifi, 廁所既地方唔好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你記住呀mon post狗<br />\n我地係被動架<br />\n如果機場旅客有咩阻滯延誤<br />\n都係因為你地唔批遊行<br />\n先搞到我地焗住入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位，be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0fd4a2edcfd43c6aeb5bb6ed01b1b24012faad","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"睇埋呢3日就知機場成效如何"},{"pid":"d42dff37c43d0dadad137473367dfad6d2489214","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推下post"},{"pid":"e2ebfed190cacb142eb7efcf0da7bea9971d8466","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"e625debfd3f36487a222737b1435ea49e9265f52","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"26af42b9a692696bb59f9e5bffaa2658d9ea327d","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"fc9b058a04fd5858eeb751279a8ab1aa90f9025d","tid":1436701,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"Any body still alive?<img src=\"/ass